summary:
I am an experienced marketing professional with a focus on developing, executing campaigns and events that drive positive outcomes. I am highly organized and capable of managing multiple projects simultaneously. I possess strong communication and collaboration skills, enabling me to work seamlessly with internal and external stakeholders. 

I have a keen interest in technology and the use of technology in marketing. I am eager to leverage the latest tools, platforms to create innovative and effective campaigns that engage, and resonate with target audiences.
